<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Resultado</title>
    <style>
        h1,
        p,
        li,
        .center {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        p {
            color: #7A7A7A;
        }

        .option {
            min-width: 300px;
            background-color: #1E20DC;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .survey {
            min-width: 300px;
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 0 15px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .coupon {
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .coupon-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <img class="logo" src="https://trulivers.com/assets/logo-line-blue-email.png" width="300">
    <h1 style="color: #1E20DC;">¡Hola <%= name %>!</h1>
    <p>Tu compra ha sido efectiva, puedes disfrutar del siguiente cupón para tu beneficio hasta su fecha de vencimiento.
    </p>
    <p>
        <%= description %>
    </p>
    <div class="coupon-container">
        <div class="coupon">
            <h1>
                <%= code %>
            </h1>
            <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=300x300&data=<%= code %>" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <p>¡Síguenos en nuestras redes!</p>
    <table style="width: 100%;">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right;">
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/trulivers.app/">
                    <img class="icon" src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3955/3955027.png" width="50">
                </a>
            </td>
            <td>
                <a
                    href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=573013735256&text=Hola,%20quiero%20saber%20m%C3%A1s%20de%20Trulivers">
                    <img class="icon" src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3955/3955040.png" width="50">
                </a>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <p>¡Descarga nuestra App!</p>
    <table style="width: 100%;">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right;">
                <a href="https://apps.apple.com/es/app/trulivers/id6446598356">
                    <img class="icon" src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/128/5977/5977575.png" width="50">
                </a>
            </td>
            <td>
                <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.truliapp">
                    <img class="icon" src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/128/300/300218.png" width="50">
                </a>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>